=\\frac{1}{-x}$ 的平移可得到 $f(x)$ ，则此时 $f(x)$ 单调递增, 作出图像如下图所示,\n\n第二步:\n令\n\n$$\ng(x)=f(x)-m x+\\frac{2}{3} m=0\n$$\n\n即\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_10_24_47a253f79e08acf28419g-26.jpg?height=429&width=577&top_left_y=314&top_left_x=1342","line":526}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"3nne2h","at":1769671154715}},"smart_blocks:01-数学教学/试卷/试卷 md 版本/功底考16题1-16套.md#科目二答题示例": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04180384,0.01255641,0.02960511,-0.05564496,0.01609344,-0.00420979,-0.01422289,-0.02907625,0.01615462,-0.00726216,0.03814009,-0.03792615,0.03031671,-0.01352913,0.01877756,0.02640326,-0.03016981,-0.0395985,-0.03638541,-0.00012596,0.12687679,-0.0439081,-0.01307403,-0.06735056,0.03400576,0.05027591,0.03887612,-0.06676139,0.01951792,-0.19567369,0.00417578,0.02450962,-0.02043655,0.02086436,0.03083874,-0.03578717,-0.00626256,0.07711598,-0.05890007,0.0372543,-0.00446228,0.06724334,0.0483021,-0.01968228,0.02729218,-0.03718331,-0.02007266,-0.03683008,0.03008552,-0.03294975,-0.05542551,-0.00706038,-0.01466137,0.0212268,0.02819007,0.00555946,-0.00035584,0.06019922,-0.01791218,-0.0048677,0.04417514,0.0303973,-0.23982556,0.02152202,0.04527445,-0.01140279,-0.00025342,-0.03835846,0.0603452,0.08777762,-0.0385407,0.00299993,0.01092881,0.04865917,0.00113326,0.00787462,0.03108186,-0.01061152,-0.04787315,-0.0365398,-0.02052352,0.06940535,0.04100067,-0.02744313,-0.00795914,0.00563245,0.01014706,-0.093121,-0.0079662,-0.04340935,-0.00573044,-0.01926479,0.0163676,0.04127743,-0.05066271,0.03316252,0.02359447,0.02590819,-0.01495858,0.09651166,-0.04469737,0.08229378,-0.00437856,-0.07534486,0.00792129,-0.034322,-0.02270949,-0.0930596,-0.00123768,-0.01578124,-0.04051138,-0.0268762,0.07775417,-0.07937801,-0.01047114,-0.01121434,0.07874143,0.02745064,-0.02431998,-0.00682164,0.03600374,0.05535309,0.04386779,-0.0231552,0.00002843,-0.07210615,0.01334459,0.00952157,0.05086124,0.04631063,0.03570623,0.00924886,0.0139765,0